---
import '../styles/global.css'
---

<h1>Welcome, you!</h1>
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-row">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h2>A short briefing</h2>
      <img
        src="/assets/sonny_face.webp"
        alt="A dithered image of Sonny Stark's face"
        class="hero-face"
      />
      <p>I'm <b>Sonny Stark</b> and you are about to enter my domain...</p>
      <p>
        ...is what I would have said if we were playing <a
          href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dungeons_%26_Dragons"
          target="_blank">Dungeons & Dragons</a
        > right now. Alas, we are not. But I'm happy to see that you found your way to the home of my
        portfolio and blog. Here you will find all the thoughts and <a href="/blog"
          >rants of my opinionated brain</a
        >
        as well as <a href="/projects">all my projects.</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are interested in how this site was built, you will find it <a
          href="/about#about-this-site">right here.</a
        > Oh, and while you're at it, and if you are interested in learning more about me, you will find
        more than you ever needed there as well. If you have any questions or would like to get in touch,
        you will find all that information <a href="/contact">right over here</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        With that being said, enjoy your stay here! When you are done, don't forget to check out <a
          href="/blogroll">these fantastic poeple</a
        > whose brilliance inspire me on a daily basis.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  h1 {
    width: 100vw;
    position: relative;
    left: 50%;
    right: 50%;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    margin-left: -50vw;
    margin-right: -50vw;

    /* Prevent any wrapping or breaking of the heading text */
    white-space: nowrap;
    word-break: keep-all;
    overflow-wrap: normal;
    hyphens: none;

    /* Fluid scaling with clamp: small minimum so it can shrink on narrow viewports */
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 3.5vw + 3.2rem, 12.55rem);

    text-shadow:
      1px 1px 0px var(--accent-primary),
      1px 2px 0px var(--accent-primary),
      1px 3px 0px var(--accent-primary),
      1px 4px 0px var(--accent-primary),
      1px 5px 0px var(--accent-primary),
      1px 6px 0px var(--accent-primary),
      1px 10px 5px rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.5),
      1px 15px 10px rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.4),
      1px 20px 30px rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.3),
      1px 25px 50px rgba(16, 16, 16, 0.2);
  }

  section {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .hero-row {
    display: flex;
  }

  .hero-text {
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .hero-face {
    float: left;
    width: clamp(220px, 20vw, 320px);
    margin: 0.5rem 0.1rem 0.1rem 0.1rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    display: block;
    shape-outside: url('/assets/sonny_face.webp');
    -webkit-shape-outside: url('/assets/sonny_face.webp');
    shape-margin: 0.9rem;
    -webkit-shape-margin: 1.3rem;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  @media (max-width: 570px) {
    .hero-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: var(--spacing-md, 1rem);
    }
    h1 {
      word-break: normal;
      overflow-wrap: normal;
      text-wrap: balance;
    }

    .hero-face {
      float: none;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-md, 1rem) 0;
      display: block;

      /* disable shape-outside on small screens (no wrapping needed) */
      shape-outside: none;
      -webkit-shape-outside: none;
      shape-margin: 0;
      -webkit-shape-margin: 0;

      /* ensure image scales cleanly across width */
      object-fit: contain;
    }
  }
</style>
